detectors.description:
Reentrancy in Contribution.preBuy() ():
	External calls:
	- amount = processPurchase(PRICE_BTCS,BTCS_PORTION_MAX - btcsPortionTotal) ()
		- ! gupToken.createToken(msg.sender,o_amount) ()
	External calls sending eth:
	- amount = processPurchase(PRICE_BTCS,BTCS_PORTION_MAX - btcsPortionTotal) ()
		- ! multisigAddress.send(msg.value) ()
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- btcsPortionTotal += amount ()
	Contribution.btcsPortionTotal () can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- Contribution.preBuy() ()
